${offset 4}${color black}${cpugraph F600AA 5000a0}
${offset 4}${font DejaVu Sans Mono:size=9}${color white}CPU: $cpu% ${color red}${cpubar 6}

${font Entopia:bold:size=12}${color 00ffae}RAM ${hr 2}
